        "text_zzWPPr": {
          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p><strong>Your Prize Options</strong></p><p>The winner has the option to forgo the featured ring and instead commission a custom-made piece up to the value of $10,000 RRP including GST from Richard James Jeweller.</p><p><strong>Featured Ring</strong></p><ul><li>A dazzling $10,000 tanzanite and diamond ring.<br/></li><li>Complimentary resizing down (up to 2 sizes).<br/></li><li>Upsizing (up to 2 sizes) available at an additional cost (quote provided by Richard James Jeweller).<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Custom-Made Jewellery</strong></p><ul><li>Commission a bespoke piece of jewellery valued up to $10,000 RRP (incl. GST).<br/></li><li>Richard James Jeweller will collaborate with the winner to create the design.<br/></li><li>Approximate production timeframe: 6 weeks from final design approval.<br/></li><li>Subject to material availability and design feasibility.<br/></li></ul><h3>Full Terms & Conditions</h3><p><strong>Eligibility</strong><br/><br/>Open to New Zealand residents aged 18 years or over.</p><p><strong>Promotion Period</strong><br/><br/>Runs from 6 October 2025 to 30 November 2025.</p><p><strong>How to Enter</strong></p><ul><li>Purchase any bottle of Mission Estate wine during the promotional period.<br/></li><li>Entrants must retain the original receipt(s) as proof of purchase.<br/></li><li>Valid entries receive one entry into the ring draw.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Draw & Notification</strong></p><ul><li>The prize draw will take place on 1 December 2025.<br/></li><li>The winner will be notified by email and/or phone.<br/></li><li>The promoter is Mission Estate Winery, 198 Church Road, Napier 4110.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Prize Options</strong><br/><br/>Winner may choose either:</p><ul><li>The $10,000 featured ring, or<br/></li><li>A custom-made piece of jewellery valued up to $10,000 RRP including GST.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Resizing</strong></p><ul><li>Complimentary downsizing of the ring (up to 2 sizes).<br/></li><li>Upsizing (up to 2 sizes) will incur an additional cost; a quote will be provided by Richard James Jeweller.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Custom-Made Option</strong></p><ul><li>Custom designs are subject to material availability and feasibility, as determined by Richard James Jeweller.<br/></li><li>Estimated timeframe for production is approximately 6 weeks from the date the final design is confirmed.<br/></li><li>Once a design is approved, no further changes may be made without potential additional costs or delays.<br/></li></ul><p><strong>Acceptance Deadline</strong><br/><br/>The winner must claim and confirm their prize (and/or begin custom design discussions) within 3 months of being notified.</p><p><strong>General Conditions</strong></p><ul><li>The prize is non-refundable, non-transferable, not exchangeable, and cannot be redeemed for cash or credit.<br/></li><li>Proof of age (18+) may be required.<br/></li><li>By entering, participants agree to be bound by these Terms and Conditions.<br/></li><li>Prize including GST.<br/></li><li>The promoter’s decision is final, and no correspondence will be entered into.<br/></li><li>Winner to arrange own travel & cover cost if progressing the custom-made option.<br/></li><li>Staff members of Mission Estate Winery & Restaurant and Richard James Jeweller and their families are not eligible to enter.</li></ul>",
            "text_style": "body"
